<HTML>
<TITLE> The Washington Watch</TITLE>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="/townhall/FRC/wash.gif" WIDTH=425 HEIGHT=125>
<H2> Opinions and Editorials</H2>

<P>
</CENTER>
<HR SIZE = 3 WIDTH = 30%><P>
 <CENTER><IMG SRC="/townhall/work.gif"WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40><p>
<B> This Site is Still Under Construction</B></CENTER>
<P>
FRC's writers and public policy analysts -- not to mention FRC President Gary 
Bauer -- are frequently published in newspapers, magazines and other publications across the United States.  These articles and editorials are read by millions
of Americans, and they have a significant impact on the course of public 
understanding of the pro-family agenda.  The following articles are available
to users of Town Hall, with the permission of their original publishers as 
noted.


<p>

&#169 1995 Persimmon IT, Inc. </HTML>
