<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT20-B39-71</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000648-B046-384</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/claremont/edit/restcon.htm 204.71.237.87 19970209083922 text/html 6818
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
