<body bgcolor=#ffffff>

<center>

   <hr noshade>

   <A HREF = "../bios.htm">Return to Staff and Fellows</A> ||
   <A HREF = "../index.html">Claremont Institute Home Page</A>

   <hr noshade>

   <H1>Glenn Ellmers</H1>

</CENTER>

<a href="mailto:EllmersG@msn.com">Glenn Ellmers</a> is a Research Fellow with the Claremont Institute. He holds a B.A. in International Relations from Boston University, 
and a Masters in Political Philosophy from the Claremont Graduate School, 
where he is currently a doctoral candidate.  Before joining the Institute he 
worked for the Republican Caucus of the California Assembly.  He has published 
articles in National Review and National Review West.

<P>

<CENTER>

   <hr noshade>

   <A HREF = "../bios.htm">Return to Staff and Fellows</A> ||
