<title>May 1996 Washington Watch Newsletter</title>

<body>

<center>
<img src="/townhall/FRC/wwatch/wwatch.gif">
</center>

<p>

Volume 7<br>
Number 7<br>
May 29, 1996

<p><hr width=60% size=3><p>

<center>
<h2>CONTENTS</h2>
</center>

<font size=+1>

<ul><ul><ul>

<a href="#least">The Least of These</a><br>
<a href="#news">News Watch</a><br>
<a href="#court">Court Watch<br>
