Believers</a><br>
<li><a href="#baer">Judge Baer to NYPD: Drop Dead!</a><br>
</ul><font size=+1>
Policy Update</font><br>
<ul type=ball><li><a href="#hawaii">Hawaii Sparks Pro-Family Revolt</a><br>
