http://www.atr.org:80/townhall/spotlights/9-18-95/rnctalk.html 204.71.237.87 19970210033703 text/html 6583
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 03:37:50 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:46 GMT
Content-length: 6400
