<DOCHDR>
http://christiandigest.com:80/grounded.htm 205.185.60.110 19970121005643 text/html 17599
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 00:55:21 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N WPO-1087)
