<html><head><TITLE>Christian Digest Magazine On-Line</title>
<meta name="keywords" content="cristianity, Christ, religion, magazines,
 magazine, family, children, books,"> 
</head>

<body BGCOLOR="#ffffcc" text="000000">
<P>Subject: Getting in God's Way

<P>There is no greater thrill than knowing you being used as a
conduit for God's blessings to the world.  When you once get
to that place, and you experience even the slightest taste
of God using you for His purposes it is so overwhelmingly 
awesome that you will wonder how you would/could choose to
be anywhere but there.  Oswald Chambers wrote, in My Utmost
for His Highest,  <P>

God made us, God loves us, and He is Calling us to Himself.
The only sane response is to obey!<P>

If you knew what God wanted you to do, you would do it with
all your heart.  Give it all up to Him, and Trust that He
will direct your path.
<P>
Shabat Shalom, Ya'll  

<P>

