<html>

<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type"
content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
<meta name="keywords"
content="cristianity, Christ, religion, magazines,
 magazine, family, children, books,">
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 2.0">
<title>Christian Digest Magazine On-Line</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFCC" text="#000000">

<p>Good book to read - Crucified by Christians</p>

<p>The author addresses the hurts, betrayals in our lives that
often come from Christians. He discusses choices we can make for
responding. One chapter that was very meaniful was the discussion
of the crucifixion. What if Christ had reacted to the betrayal,
abandonment, lonliness, with bitterness and unforgiveness . . .?
Author discusses the darkness that surfaces in our lives through
hurts and the opportunity to deal with it and crucify our natural
responses. When we do that, we grow in Christ and become more
whole.<br>
<br>
</p>

