<body bgcolor="#FFFFCC" text="#000000">

<p>Subject: Spread The Word </p>

<p>One of the ways we share our faith is through our
presentations and seminars on family communication and bonding.
The chance to do this in our lives is a gift from God. And we try
to do His work through our God given talents in experiential
education. . The most rewarding for us are the parent-teenanger
adventures. There is so much discussion and openness - it is
fantastic to watch. </p>

