<meta name="keywords" content="cristianity, Christ, religion, magazines,
 magazine, family, children, books,"> 
</head>

<body BGCOLOR="#ffffcc" text="000000">

<P>Mere Christianity by C. S. Lewis
<p>
Mere Christianity by C.S. Lewis is a very useful book which
presents a nondenominational look at the basic premises of
Christianity.  This book which is for intelligent thinking
people presents Biblical truths in a modern setting.  Although
the book was written many years ago, it is still in print and 
is considered by many people to be a Christian classic.

