<P>I have recently returned to the Lord. I have been backslid for about 12 years. I had no idea what dark forces that I had opened myself up to. I got involved in some very dark things. My testimony is that Jesus is greater than all the darkness of Satan, and has overcome the Kingdom of Satan for anyone who calls upon His name.

<P>14 years ago I was divorced from my wife of 17 years and thought I had lost my children forever. I had very limited contact with them. My daughter returned to the Lord and began praying for me. One evening her Pastor asked if anyone knew some one by the name of Farrell and gave her a message for 
me. After that it didn't take long for God to work a miracle in my life and deliver me from my involvement in the Occult.

<P>My family and my salvation has been restored. I know have a daughter and a son that I thought I had lost forever.

<P>If anyone reads this, I live in Highland Calif, and attend New Life Fellowship. I would enjoy making some new Christian Cyberfriends. EMail me at <A HREF="mailto:FarrellH@genesisnetwork.net">FarrellH@genesisnetwork.net</A>.

