<DOCOLDNO>IA070-000445-B015-48</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://christiandigest.com:80/forum/qaMsg5.htm 205.185.60.110 19970121012030 text/html 1867
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 01:19:11 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N WPO-1087)
Allow-ranges: bytes
Content-type: text/html
