<head>
<title>Christian Digest Magazine On-Line</title>
<meta name="keywords" content="christianity, Christ, religion, magazines,
 magazine, family, children, books,">
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFCC" text="#000000">
<p>Subject: Day of worship
<p>It is my understanding that the Sabbath was Saturday, as  practiced by 
the Jews. After Christ rose from the grave on a Sunday, the early Christians 
changed their day of worship, or the Sabbath, to Sunday.
 
</p>
