<p>Subject: Literal Interpretation of the Bible. </p>

<p>I believe in Jesus Christ, yet I cannot reconcile the apparent
contradictions of the Bible. There are so many to point out, such
as two creation stories, two flood stories etc... Do I have
suspend my rational thinking in order to accept Jesus Christ? I
don't think so yet so many I speak with demand that I accept,
word for word, the authenticity of the entire bible? Opinions?
Help? </p>

