<p>Subject: fear</p>

<p>My wife and I have been married for 20 years. In all that time
we have struggled with communication. She has over the last 4-6
years totally moved away from me emotionally. She won't talk...
this problem goes back to the beginning of our relationship and
before.. can anyone out there point me to anything on the
internet about the fear of confrontations? I believe my wife is
trapped in fear that she can't deal with and I don't know how to
help her. </p>

<p>E-mail me <a href="mailto:vmyucha@olypen.com">vmyucha@olypen.com</a>
thanks Bill</p>

