<P>Does anyone have a comment on my dad getting remarried and having our family picture taken.  All my brothers and I are getting together for the first time in about ten years, and I would like a family picture of them and the nieces but Dad remarried last week.  Should we include Dad--I think so but I don't want any hard feelings,  either from Dad or Mom or or my brothers.  No one wants to feel excluded but then
I don't want anyone to be uncomfortable.  I would like a picture with all members in it so that we have a nice time line; but not if we all have long faces.

<P>Comments, please.

