<DOCHDR>
http://christiandigest.com:80/forum/qaMsg72.htm 205.185.60.110 19970121013154 text/html 2685
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 01:30:24 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N WPO-1087)
Allow-ranges: bytes
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Tuesday, 31-Dec-96 00:07:02 GMT
