<p>Subject: Family</p>

<p>As Christians, our family extends beyond blood. As a woman,
married, divorced, and remarried, having been raised in a blended
family, and also trying to put one together; acceptance is the
issue. God accepts us as we are. We are to be brothers and
sisters in Him. However, one good choice to make is have just
brothers and sisters in one, and dad with you all in another. I
am sure you are on the right track. 1 John 4:7-8 Merry Christmas </p>

