<p>Subject: love is a decision, and God can help </p>

<p>You say you don't love your wife well enough, Who are you to
say that? God can love her through you just ask Him to, then
you'll be giving her the very very best. Just decide, (which I
think you did when you married her) that you want to love her,
and let God work through you. Of course this will also strengthen
your own walk with God, as you learn to lean on Him for strength
and guidance in your EVERYDAY life. </p>

