<p>Subject: Divorce Depression</p>

<p>We know what pain you are going through, having both gone
through the break up of our first Marriages. Healing is very
slow, and you often receive little support from the church or
other Christians...they just don't know how to handle the thorny
issue of divorce. We are currently working with a young operation
known as DivorceCare. perhaps there may be a group meeting
somewhere near you. If not, perhaps as you heal, you may be able
to help others suffering your grief. It is not easy recovering
from the trauma of the tearing apart of the &quot;One Flesh&quot;
of a marriage. Our prayers are with you.<br>
<br>
</p>

