<DOCHDR>
http://christiandigest.com:80/forum/qaMsg4.htm 205.185.60.110 19970121015949 text/html 3139
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 01:58:39 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N WPO-1087)
Allow-ranges: bytes
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Monday, 11-Nov-96 20:09:55 GMT
